_sText: The map has sniper spots in the spawn.  Six Awps in the map so once there gone they are gone!  It has buy zones so if your server allows the purchase of awps then go ahead.  The map has a underground maze with you can climb down into and fight inside your maze or make your way to climb out right next to the enemy spawn.  It has some mid-field protection for cover.  A floor in the middle for cover.
